==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forbidden
<hw>For*bid"den</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Prohibited;
interdicted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I know no spells, use no <qex>forbidden</qex> arts.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Forbidden fruit</b></col>. <sd>(a)</sd> <cd>Any coveted
unlawful pleasure, -- so called with reference to the forbidden fruit of
the Garden of Eden.</cd> <sd>(b)</sd> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <cd>A small
variety of shaddock (<spn>Citrus decumana</spn>). The name is given in
different places to several varieties of Citrus fruits.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forbiddenly</ent>⟦br⟧
